Kahekili bottle data, July 2025

Sites

Six sites (Seep, S1-S4, Control) were sampled for nutrients and carbonate chemistry. Samples were collected (n = 6) at daytime (both high and low tide), and nighttime low tide for two days.

Summary plots

Boxplots of each parameter per site. Y-axis is in log-scale. Sites are arranged from the Seep to the Control site. Red circles denote mean value, grey circles denote individual data points, black circles denote outliers.
